        FROM [Transactions] AS [t]
        WHERE [t].[UserIdentityId] = @__userId_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END

FROM [Transactions] AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Currencies] AS [c] ON [t].[CurrencyId] = [c].[Id]
